&lt;p data-start=&quot;654&quot; data-end=&quot;728&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;654&quot; data-end=&quot;686&quot;&gt;Functional Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;686&quot; data-end=&quot;689&quot;&gt;As part of Case Management, you will:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul data-start=&quot;729&quot; data-end=&quot;1577&quot;&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;729&quot; data-end=&quot;810&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;731&quot; data-end=&quot;810&quot;&gt;Take actions to improve on-time delivery, quality, and customer satisfaction.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;811&quot; data-end=&quot;891&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;813&quot; data-end=&quot;891&quot;&gt;Track and monitor the progress of multiple customer orders and partner jobs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;892&quot; data-end=&quot;1021&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;894&quot; data-end=&quot;1021&quot;&gt;Provide excellent customer and partner service through relationship-building, partnership creation, and timely order updates.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1022&quot; data-end=&quot;1158&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1024&quot; data-end=&quot;1158&quot;&gt;Apply technical knowledge (or leverage subject matter experts) on manufacturing design and production to ensure timely job delivery.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1159&quot; data-end=&quot;1316&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1161&quot; data-end=&quot;1316&quot;&gt;Understand supplier capabilities and execute supplier oversight, including phone assessments, schedule creation, quality reviews, and corrective actions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1317&quot; data-end=&quot;1434&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1319&quot; data-end=&quot;1434&quot;&gt;Assess the impact of manufactured part rejections and communicate with suppliers and customers to resolve issues.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1435&quot; data-end=&quot;1500&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1437&quot; data-end=&quot;1500&quot;&gt;Manage customer complaints resulting in product replacements.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1501&quot; data-end=&quot;1577&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1503&quot; data-end=&quot;1577&quot;&gt;Report status, risks, and recovery efforts for troubled orders and jobs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1579&quot; data-end=&quot;1596&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;1579&quot; data-end=&quot;1594&quot;&gt;Job Duties:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul data-start=&quot;1597&quot; data-end=&quot;2221&quot;&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1597&quot; data-end=&quot;1652&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1599&quot; data-end=&quot;1652&quot;&gt;Document all case activity in the central database.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1653&quot; data-end=&quot;1740&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1655&quot; data-end=&quot;1740&quot;&gt;Utilize company technology platforms and comply with the Quality Management System.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1741&quot; data-end=&quot;1795&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1743&quot; data-end=&quot;1795&quot;&gt;Monitor the integrity of supplier quality metrics.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Xometry (NASDAQ: XMTR) powers the industries of today and tomorrow by connecting the people with big ideas to the manufacturers who can bring them to life. Xometry’s digital marketplace gives manufacturers the critical resources they need to grow their business while also making it easy for buyers at Fortune 1000 companies to tap into global manufacturing capacity.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Recruiter will be responsible for executing the day-to-day recruiting activities, managing the candidate experience, and collaborating with hiring managers to fill open roles in a timely and efficient manner. The Recruiter will also play a key role in promoting the company’s employer brand and ensuring a consistent recruitment process.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;End-to-End Recruitment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage the full recruitment lifecycle for assigned roles, including sourcing, screening, interviewing, and presenting candidates to hiring managers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate the interview process, scheduling, and feedback collection to ensure a smooth experience for candidates and hiring managers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support onboarding activities for new hires to ensure a positive start at the company.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sourcing and Talent Pool Development&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Utilise a variety of sourcing methods (e.g., LinkedIn, job boards, networking events) to identify and engage potential candidates.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain a strong pipeline of qualified candidates for current and future hiring needs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with the Senior Talent Acquisition and Brand Specialist to implement targeted sourcing strategies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Candidate Relationship Management&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as the main point of contact for candidates throughout the recruitment process, ensuring timely and professional communication.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Foster positive relationships with candidates to build a network of talent that aligns with the company’s culture and hiring needs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Gather and provide feedback to candidates, regardless of the hiring decision, to maintain a positive employer brand.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Employer Branding Support&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist in promoting the company’s employer brand by sharing content on social media, participating in career fairs, and attending networking events.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure job postings are appealing, accurate, and reflect the company’s values and culture.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support recruitment marketing initiatives led by the Senior Talent Acquisition and Brand Specialist.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Recruitment Metrics and Continuous Improvement&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track key recruitment metrics, such as time-to-fill and candidate satisfaction, to measure recruitment effectiveness.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Suggest process improvements to enhance the efficiency and quality of the recruitment function.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay updated on industry trends and best practices to bring fresh ideas to the team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Skills and Competencies&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sourcing and Recruiting Skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to identify and attract talent through various sourcing techniques.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong interviewing skills to assess candidates’ skills and cultural fit.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Organisational Skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exceptional organisational abilities to manage multiple open roles and candidates simultaneously.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Attention to detail in maintaining accurate candidate records and tracking recruitment activities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comm

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Xometry (NASDAQ: XMTR) powers the industries of today and tomorrow by connecting the people with big ideas to the manufacturers who can bring them to life. Xometry’s digital marketplace gives manufacturers the critical resources they need to grow their business while also making it easy for buyers at Fortune 1000 companies to tap into global manufacturing capacity.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;For our Sales Team department we are looking for a &lt;strong&gt;Molding&amp;amp;Casting Engineer&lt;/strong&gt; with immediate effect to further expand our business. You will support or manage complex and critical projects and work with internal teams, customers and production. In addition to working with customers and production partners, you will actively shape your work environment and collaborate with all critical interfaces. Good ideas are implemented quickly at our company and do not have to go through various steering committees or management meetings to be reviewed several times, checked again and then perhaps decided upon. Your working day is exciting and varied, the environment is international.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyzing incoming 3D CAD part design for Injection Molding, other tooling technologies;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Check Injection Molding Design for Manufacturing (DFM) reports and challenge manufacturer’s technical solutions;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicate with external customers via video calls and explain DFM reports/gather feedback and discuss technical solutions with manufacturers across Europe and Asia;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;To optimize part 3D CAD design and improve part design feasibility issues, if necessary;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in meetings to fix quality claims for Injection Molding, High Pressure Die Casting, other tooling technologies together with a cross-functional team and external customers;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Attend pre-sales meetings with Sales Team and external customers via video-calls,&amp;nbsp; support technical questions/answers for potential projects.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A successful candidate:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Higher engineering education - thermoplastic processing engineer, plastic part design engineer, mechanical design engineer (automotive interior, IoT devices, similar);&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in an engineering role on a production floor with plastic processing&amp;nbsp; OR in a development of parts suitable for molding/casting processing;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Expert knowledge of thermoplastic processing: plastic part design rules for a feasible injection molding processing, injection molding tool design basic structure and design, thermoplastic processing most common quality issues and root causes, understanding of Mold Flow analysis and it results,&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understanding of various plastic post-processes: pad-printing, silk-screening, spray painting, chroming, hot foil stamping, etc&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of other tooling technologies like Vacuum Casting in silicone molds, Compression Molding, Investment Casting, Sand Casting, Metal Injection Molding will be a benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong multicultural communication skills in English with ability to convince, justify and defend ideas and technical solutions in front of external / internal stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Working conditions:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Remote full-time job.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Working hours according to Central European Time (start / end is negotiable)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fixed rate depending on the career level.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Significant annual loyalty bonus.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Overtime hours are possible for this position.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Corporate Laptop, 3D CAD software.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt

