&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We are looking for a Sales Engineer&lt;/strong&gt; who will strengthen our Sales team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Functional responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Technical Sales Support:&lt;/strong&gt; Serve as the primary technical resource for the sales team, delivering expert advice and support throughout the sales process.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Solution Design: &lt;/strong&gt;Collaborate with clients and internal teams to understand requirements and design tailored technical solutions that meet customer needs and align with our capabilities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Client Engagement:&lt;/strong&gt; Participate in client meetings and presentations, providing technical insights and resolving queries to build trust and secure business.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sales Team Training: &lt;/strong&gt;Develop and deliver training programs to enhance the sales team’s understanding of technical concepts and manufacturing processes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cross-Functional Collaboration:&lt;/strong&gt; Work with the Engineering, Product Management, and Customer Support teams to ensure seamless integration of solutions and enhance overall service offerings.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Technical Documentation: &lt;/strong&gt;Create and maintain comprehensive documentation for technical solutions, processes, and client requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Continuous Improvement&lt;/strong&gt;: Stay updated with industry trends and advancements to continually improve technical offerings and propose innovative solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Requirements for applicants:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Graduate engineering degree.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div&gt;4+ years of experience in metalworking / mechanical engineering.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Expert knowledge of various metalworking methods: CNC machining, sheet metal working, 3D printing.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Good knowledge of Italian and English.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div&gt;IT enthusiast, ready to master and use modern technologies and software.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Willingness and desire to work in a fast-growing business atmosphere.&lt;/div&gt;
